    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Hatch-vcs Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>Hatch_vcs</application> is a Hatch plugin for versioning
        with several <xref linkend="gVCS"/>.
      </para>

      &lfs120_checked;

